Use this to clear the value of one path-info position; if no position is specified, the entire path-info component is cleared.

<code type="php">
$uri = Solar::factory('Solar_Uri');
$uri->import('http://example.com/index.php/more/path/info';
// now $uri->info is array('more', 'path', 'info');

// let's clear position 1
$uri->clearInfo(1);
// now $uri->info is array('more', 'info');

// let's clear everything
$uri->clearInfo();
// now $uri->info is array()
</code>